    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You establish a telepathic link with one &amp;Reference[beast]{beast} you touch that is friendly to you or &amp;Reference[charmed]{charmed} by you. The spell fails if the beastâ€™s &amp;Reference[int]{Intelligence} is 4 or higher. Until the spell ends, the link is active while you and the &amp;Reference[beast]{beast} are within &amp;Reference[line]{line} of sight of each other. Through the link, the &amp;Reference[beast]{beast} can understand your telepathic messages to it, and it can telepathically communicate simple emotions and concepts back to you. While the link is active, the &amp;Reference[beast]{beast} gains advantage on attack rolls against any creature within 5 feet of you that you can see.</p>\n</div>",
